data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT BY $145K+!!! Welcome to premier living in the coveted Seminole Lake Golf and Country Club. This deeded golf corner lot home sits right at the 9th tee box and was previously owned by a custom builder who designed a beautiful & unique home with a nice blend of luxury, comfort, and style and many upgraded extras. Just minutes away from top beaches such as Indian Shores, Redington, Madeira, Indian Rocks, and other iconic beaches!    This home checks so many boxes. 4 bedrooms, 4 full bathrooms, great outdoor entertaining of an additional 1,500 sq ft, an elevator, 2 tranquil ponds and a wonderful balcony off the primary bedroom for a stunning morning and evening view.   You'll be welcomed to your 4,512 sq ft home by its large paver circular drive and lush garden which sets the stage for what lies within.      Enter the great room with elevated 25' soaring ceilings, designer finishes, a loft & behind double French doors off the great room a covered lanai with pond. This creates a visually stunning and inviting effect, but also provides an airy and spacious feel.     Culinary greatness awaits you in the kitchen featuring an expansive central island, an abundance of cabinetry, stainless steel appliances and granite counters. The kitchen opens to the formal dining room, family room and breakfast room. Whether you are having a casual dinner with family, or a formal dinner party, you have the perfect space for all.     Enjoy the best of our Florida lifestyle with a resort-styled lanai which seamlessly connects to the oversized family room with pocket sliders to truly enjoy the indoor/outdoor living we all love in Florida revealing a spectacular outdoor tiled space with a large covered entertaining area. An area which holds 2 pizza ovens, kegerator and beverage refrigerator. All screened in where you can relax & bask in the beauty of the golf course and amazing sunset in the evenings & enjoy the refreshing breeze as you unwind or entertain guests.     Take the spiral staircase or elevator upstairs to the primary bedroom which is ~ 830 sq ft, tinted glass sliding doors that open to your 300 sq ft screened porch & 200 sq ft open balcony overlooking the golf course and its beautiful views. Primary bath features a glass enclosed shower & soaker tub ideal for a spa like experience, dual sinks and tray ceiling.    A second owners suite is located in the private wing on the first floor.     The game room off the family room has a pool table, wet bar, complete with a wine and beverage refrigerator, sink, built in cabinetry and granite counters. A Jack & Jill modern & lux bathroom connects to the 3rd bedroom. The 4th bedroom has an en-suite private bathroom as well or turn it into an office, zen fitness room or home library. Completing this impressive residence is a laundry room located off the attached 2- car garage with custom cabinetry.     Updates include: ROOF-2016, 2 NEW AC UNITS-2021, WATER HEATER-2021, INTERIOR PAINT-2021, SURROUND SOUND SYSTEM-2021  Country Club membership is available with golf, pool, tennis courts & kayak launch into the Bayou. This home is truly breathtaking! Don’t hesitate, schedule your private showing today.
